This is the quintessential Greek oregano, a direct descendant of sun-baked Mediterranean hillsides, now stabilized for unparalleled potency and productivity in an urban environment. ‘OG-35’ delivers the robust, peppery, and slightly bitter flavour that is the undisputed king of pizza, pasta, and grilled meats, with an aromatic intensity that stands up to prolonged cooking.

